@startuml
skinparam backgroundColor white
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam defaultFontName "Helvetica"
skinparam defaultFontSize 13
skinparam activityBorderColor black
skinparam activityBackgroundColor white
skinparam activityDiamondBorderColor black
skinparam activityDiamondBackgroundColor white
skinparam arrowColor black
skinparam noteBorderColor black
skinparam noteBackgroundColor white
skinparam partitionBorderColor black
skinparam partitionBackgroundColor #F5F5F5

title Automated Research Evaluation — Process Flow

|#F5F5F5|  **Human (one-time setup)**  |
start
:Define **Research Scope**
  6 hypotheses, 11 scenarios;
:Build **Evaluation Scorecard**
  18 criteria, weighted (5x / 3x / 2x);
:Write **Evaluation Prompt**
  197 lines: research phases,
  scoring rules, source integrity;
:List **10 Candidates**
  in markdown table (queue);

|#white|  **Bash Loop (automated)**  |
:Start loop iteration;

repeat
  :Claude Code reads
  candidate list;
  :Pick first platform,
  remove from list;

  |#F5F5F5|  **Claude Code session (fresh context)**  |
  :Phase 1 — Official sources
  docs, product pages, changelogs;
  :Phase 2 — Technical capabilities
  APIs, integrations, architecture;
  :Phase 3 — Community evidence
  reviews, GitHub issues, forums;
  :Phase 4 — Pricing
  plans, licensing, TCO;
  :Score 18 criteria
  against rubrics with sources;
  :Assess 11 scenarios
  + validate 6 hypotheses;
  :Save evaluation file
  (YAML frontmatter + citations);

  |#white|  **Bash Loop (automated)**  |
repeat while (candidates remaining?) is (yes)
-> no;

|#F5F5F5|  **Output**  |
:10 evaluation files
  ~73,000 words
  371 source citations;
:Obsidian Dataview dashboard
  auto-generates comparison tables;
stop

@enduml
